  "detailed_description": "In Runemancer you play the vital role of a healer, the cornerstone of any adventurer group. Your mission is to support your allies by skillfully combining runes to amplify their abilities.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603590/extras/f072c01d1045dfde94d8ff13ab25dab1.poster.avif?t=1702553609\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603590/extras/f072c01d1045dfde94d8ff13ab25dab1.webm?t=1702553609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603590/extras/f072c01d1045dfde94d8ff13ab25dab1.mp4?t=1702553609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br><i>Empower Your Allies</i>: As the healer, your expertise lies in combining runes to enhance your comrades' capabilities. Turn the tide of battle by strategically boosting their strength and ensuring their survival.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603590/extras/1061476a932782da8794b608ad25c47f.poster.avif?t=1702553609\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603590/extras/1061476a932782da8794b608ad25c47f.webm?t=1702553609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603590/extras/1061476a932782da8794b608ad25c47f.mp4?t=1702553609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>Choose Your Path</i>: You have the opportunity to select new abilities as you progress through the game. Your choices are crucial, shaping your character's development and determining your party's destiny. Pick your abilities wisely based on the unique build you envision for your team.<br><br><i>Wave-Based Challenges</i>: Runemancer offers an exciting wave-based gameplay experience, with each stage presenting distinct challenges. Face off against hordes of formidable enemies and adapt your strategies as you progress through the game's dynamic stages.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603590/extras/8f752bd80865b67a6319995dfd6cb9ae.poster.avif?t=1702553609\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603590/extras/8f752bd80865b67a6319995dfd6cb9ae.webm?t=1702553609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603590/extras/8f752bd80865b67a6319995dfd6cb9ae.mp4?t=1702553609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Prepare to embark on an epic adventure as the healer in Runemancer. Your decisions will be the key to success as you empower your allies and guide them to victory in this thrilling wave-based RPG.",
  "about_the_game": "In Runemancer you play the vital role of a healer, the cornerstone of any adventurer group. Your mission is to support your allies by skillfully combining runes to amplify their abilities.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603590/extras/f072c01d1045dfde94d8ff13ab25dab1.poster.avif?t=1702553609\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603590/extras/f072c01d1045dfde94d8ff13ab25dab1.webm?t=1702553609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603590/extras/f072c01d1045dfde94d8ff13ab25dab1.mp4?t=1702553609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br><i>Empower Your Allies</i>: As the healer, your expertise lies in combining runes to enhance your comrades' capabilities. Turn the tide of battle by strategically boosting their strength and ensuring their survival.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603590/extras/1061476a932782da8794b608ad25c47f.poster.avif?t=1702553609\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603590/extras/1061476a932782da8794b608ad25c47f.webm?t=1702553609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603590/extras/1061476a932782da8794b608ad25c47f.mp4?t=1702553609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>Choose Your Path</i>: You have the opportunity to select new abilities as you progress through the game. Your choices are crucial, shaping your character's development and determining your party's destiny. Pick your abilities wisely based on the unique build you envision for your team.<br><br><i>Wave-Based Challenges</i>: Runemancer offers an exciting wave-based gameplay experience, with each stage presenting distinct challenges. Face off against hordes of formidable enemies and adapt your strategies as you progress through the game's dynamic stages.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603590/extras/8f752bd80865b67a6319995dfd6cb9ae.poster.avif?t=1702553609\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603590/extras/8f752bd80865b67a6319995dfd6cb9ae.webm?t=1702553609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603590/extras/8f752bd80865b67a6319995dfd6cb9ae.mp4?t=1702553609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Prepare to embark on an epic adventure as the healer in Runemancer. Your decisions will be the key to success as you empower your allies and guide them to victory in this thrilling wave-based RPG.",
